summary: An ordinance relating to and providing for the payment of the sum of Three Hundred Thirty-seven and 29/100 ($337.29) Dollars, decreed to be paid by the City in a decree of the Superior Court of Washington, for King County, rendered in Probate Proceeding No. 30871, entitled "In the Matter of the Estate of Helen V. Denny, Deceased," and making an appropriation from the General Fund therefor.
